`★ Insight ─────────────────────────────────────`
- Delta-only persistence is the key innovation: unexplored chunks cost zero storage because they're regenerated from seed. Only chunks the player actually modifies get diff entries.
- Legend State observables work in-memory (no SQLite needed) in tests — the same `chunkDiffs$` observable used in production can be directly reset via `clearAllChunkDiffs()` in `beforeEach`.
- The diff `apply` function must reconstruct the full `TreeComponent` struct with all required fields even though the diff only stores a minimal subset — defaults fill the gaps.
`─────────────────────────────────────────────────`
